ilaq ad yi-tɛawnem bac ad ten-id-sellkeɣ
ur tzeggel ara ula d yiwet
ḥewwes ahat ad tafeḍ agerruj yeččuren d idrimen
mačči d tamsalt teɛǧeb-iyi neɣ ayen-nniḍen
acḥal ur d-rzin imeslayen am wi ɣer umeẓẓuɣ-is
d acu ad ak-d-awiɣ ad tesweḍ
d acu i as-d-yeḍleb ad yexdem
am wakken ur ttmeslayen ara yiwet n tutlayt
ad tafeḍ ugaden akk ad ten-ṭṭef lehwa
d tidet ur issin ara ad iɛumm tom
twalaḍ amek ur yettak ara yidir afus di newwara
sliman u muḥ ur yezmir ara ad yerr i tiziri tagawawt
sima yuɛer-as lḥal ad tessuffeɣ ayen yellan deg wul-is
imeslayen ur xuṣṣen ara d ibaḥanen wulmen gerrzen
ilaq-as kan ad d-yeccetki ɣef kra
tekcem tejmeɛ-d lqecc-is teffeɣ-d ɣer ɣur-s
ɣas ulamma yeqɛed ad s-d-afen ccama
wid ixeddmen leqder d lḥerma i yixxamen-nsen
di ṣṣbeḥ kan i ḥemmleɣ ad sweɣ lqahwa
gguleɣ ur d-iris ufus n urgaz fell-i ma ur iyi-ihwi ara
faḍel yeḥbes ur itess ara ddwa-ines dɣa uɣalen-as-d leṣwat-nni
ḥsen u muḥ yuɣ-d kukayin ɣer tiziri tagawawt
ad yerbeḥ yes-s ad yernu wid yuḥwaǧen
neɣ ahat tbeddel s wayen lɛali
zgan ttqisin-tt s zzin-is d tfekka-s
akken uɣen tanumi yal mi ara d-yali wass
ad iṭṭef rebbi ayen yugaren aya
yettu d akken mi ara faken lehdur
sserḥ-as akken i ak-yehwa ad d-yezzi alamma d ɣur-k
anwa ara d-yerren talwit i tmurt tura
d acu i d-tlemdeḍ ar uselmad-ik
asenfar-ik yelha maca ṣṣeḥ d wa  wissen mi ad aɣ-d-yawi ugar n urmud
ur ssinen ara ad uraren ddabex
mačči d ayen ara k-d-iṣiḥen akk
ini-d d acu i twalaḍ deg taluft-a
tafunast-nneɣ tecneg d ayefki tebzeg tmaẓẓagt-is yiwen yiff ineggi d azarig
d allen n wefṛux i tesɛa
ma ur teẓdimeḍ ara ur k-id-ittṣaḥ wara
tella-d tmezgunt tidak n nna fa
tura tella tin izedɣen ul n urgaz-agi
asenɛet n yisura d umeslay fell-asen
seg tufɣa n laɛqel i deg i tella ur tefriẓ ara abrid
dɣa iswi-nsen d amek ara yeḥrez umdan tawennaḍt anda yettidir
baɛed akin nnefs-im ihebbej deg wulawen-nneɣ
rnu argaz-im ur yettɛeṭil ara ad m-ibru
sers dinna asenduq n cchada ssedreg-it s uɣummu
ahat yeẓra ur sɛiɣ ara yir cufat
twalaḍ tida mi d-usant ih walaɣ-tent
siwel neɣ qim ulac win ara d-yeslen
teddiḍ-d ula deg yidlisen n yimusnawen
ur ilaq ad nettu yelli-s n inuba d nettat kan i yesɛa
ad tefkem i umeɣlal asfel i tečča tmes
ad xedmen kullec am wakken i k-t-id-umṛeɣ
imawlan n zahra ṭṭfen di ddin mačči d kra
ad txedmeḍ snat n txelxalin n ddheb ɣef yiran n ufella n tbanta
ad am-iẓẓu ṛebbi tigusa deg uxxam-im
neɣ yella deg wacu irewsent d wayen i mgaradent
acimi ur tettɣimad ara ad tensed
agellid yenna-yas deg awal-is  a tagelliḍt ur umineɣ s tgeldunt d ugeldun
am mmi-s n dda remḍan yefkan idrimen deg wurḍan
ad yuɣal udeffel di tazwara d ddurt id iteddun
amasay n ugezdu n ufares di steel yugi ad d-yazen tarrayt n ufares n yifarisen icudden ar wuzzal
akken i tt-tessewweḍ mliḥ ara tibnin
ad yettweḥḥed deg umkerwa war nnger n tzizwa deg tafukt akked yiǧeǧǧigen deg yidis n temguṭ zegzawen
a wi hedṛen alama d ṣbeḥ ɣef igrawliwen iqbayliyen
aḥṛiq i d-yeǧǧa baba yuɣal d tiẓgi
addag-nni yugi ad yernu ad yimɣur
ad teǧǧuǧgeḍ ad trennuḍ akken i nebɣa ad kem-nwali
acuɣeṛ ur tettɣamam ara amkan-nni d ilem
a wi yerran tudert akk d turart
ad d-tbineḍ am tungift ma telsiḍ taqendurt n yemma-m
akken ad yeffer lbaḍna ur tt-ẓerren deg udrar ideg d-tṣubbeḍ aqjun yif-ik ɣur-sen
ad yewwet udeffel deg uzgen n ddurt id iteddun
akken ad tlemmedeḍ tameslayt ilaq ad tissineḍ taseftit n yimyagen
acuɣeṛ i s ulac win i yi-ittamnen
agraw n tigejda n teqbaylit ggten deg-s imeẓdaren d yimeɣnasen
akken nebda asileɣ iḥbes-as i yuba uselkim-is dɣa nessiwel i takfarinas amasay n ugezdu n tsenselkimt di steel
aɣyul d aɣyul ur yettuɣal d izem
